# ============================================
# DEPLOYMENT CHECKLIST
# ============================================
# 
# FOR VERCEL DEPLOYMENT:
# 1. Don't commit .env.local or .env.production with real values
# 2. Set all NEXT_PUBLIC_* variables on Vercel Dashboard:
#    Settings → Environment Variables
# 3. Set for all environments: Production, Preview, Development
# 4. Use Railway backend URL for NEXT_PUBLIC_API_BASE_URL
# 
# AFTER VERCEL DEPLOYMENT:
# 1. Get your Vercel production URL
# 2. Update Railway backend environment variables:
#    - CORS_ORIGIN=https://your-vercel-app.vercel.app,https://your-vercel-app-*.vercel.app
#    - FRONTEND_URL=https://your-vercel-app.vercel.app
#    - PAYOS_RETURN_URL=https://your-vercel-app.vercel.app/customer/payment/success
#    - PAYOS_CANCEL_URL=https://your-vercel-app.vercel.app/customer/payment/cancel
# 3. Railway will auto-redeploy with updated CORS settings
# 4. Test integration: frontend ↔ backend
# 
